      "writtenOn": "2026-07-23T14:56:35Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Why do you need the associations ? \nWhy can\u0027t it just sit at the same path like https://github.com/openbmc/phosphor-dbus-interfaces/blob/341308f4b6e8fcb962a572d274153ca269703ba2/yaml/xyz/openbmc_project/State/Decorator/OperationalStatus.interface.yaml#L4",
      "revId": "087d3d9ca4735325d0753902c73a9f09fd079614",
      "serverId": "adbd0a64-1f21-4d83-b585-671fe73cb6e4"
    },
    {
